import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['Effect_Amount_of_damage'] = pd.to_numeric(data['Effect_Amount_of_damage'], errors='coerce')
    data = data.dropna(subset=['Effect_Amount_of_damage'])
    sns.histplot(data=data, x='Effect_Amount_of_damage', kde=True, color='blue')
    plt.axvline(data['Effect_Amount_of_damage'].median(), color='red', linestyle='dashed', linewidth=2, label='Median: {:.2f}'.format(data['Effect_Amount_of_damage'].median()))
    plt.legend()
    return plt

chart = plot(data)

import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['Effect_Amount_of_damage'] = pd.to_numeric(data['Effect_Amount_of_damage'], errors='coerce')
    data = data.groupby('Wildlife_Species')['Effect_Amount_of_damage'].sum().reset_index()
    data = data.sort_values(by='Effect_Amount_of_damage', ascending=False)
    chart = sns.barplot(x='Wildlife_Species', y='Effect_Amount_of_damage', data=data)
    chart.axhline(data['Effect_Amount_of_damage'].max(), color='red', linestyle='--', label='Max: {:.2f}'.format(data['Effect_Amount_of_damage'].max()))
    chart.legend(loc='upper right')
    plt.xticks(rotation=90)
    return chart

chart = plot(data)

import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['Flight_Date'] = pd.to_datetime(data['Flight_Date'], format='%Y-%m-%d', errors='coerce')
    data = data.groupby(['Flight_Date'])['count'].sum().reset_index()
    chart = sns.lineplot(x='Flight_Date', y='count', data=data)
    chart.axhline(y=data['count'].median(), color='r', linestyle='--', label='Median Count: {:.2f}'.format(data['count'].median()))
    chart.legend(loc='upper left')
    plt.title('What is the trend in the number of wildlife strikes over time?', wrap=True)
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['Flight_Date'] = pd.to_datetime(data['Flight_Date'], format='%m/%d/%Y', errors='coerce')
    data = data.dropna(subset=['Flight_Date'])
    data['Year'] = data['Flight_Date'].dt.year
    data = data.groupby(['Aircraft_Make_Model']).size().reset_index(name='count')
    data = data.sort_values(by=['count'], ascending=False)
    plt.figure(figsize=(12, 6))
    ax = sns.barplot(x='Aircraft_Make_Model', y='count', data=data, palette='Blues_d')
    ax.set_xticklabels(ax.get_xticklabels(), rotation=90, ha="right")
    ax.set_xlabel('Aircraft Make Model')
    ax.set_ylabel('Count')
    ax.axhline(y=data['count'].max(), color='r', linestyle='--', label='Max Count: {:.2f}'.format(data['count'].max()))
    ax.legend()
    return plt

chart = plot(data)
